{"tid":1402711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發其想 不如整個十八區街坊齊發夢？","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:52:45.000Z","uid":189671,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d49b802b4da443f6ca99e89b391c1592064d03","tid":1402711,"uid":189671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:49:03.000Z","msg":"經過今晚，發覺一嚟民區班狗唔會太敢亂嚟，比著今晚黃大仙嘅事發生喺金鐘等地方，班狗仲唔射到我地仆街？<br />\n<br />\n二嚟如果真係做得成十八區，自己去翻自己嗰區發夢，就可以分散狗力，我地亦唔需要話特別多人，一區有幾千個都夠！完美達到be water嘅極致！<br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲難去實行，但我相信連登仔同香港人嘅號召力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係突然之間有個諗法想講出嚟，<br />\n覺得work嘅比個正皮，覺得唔work嘅一齊討論下吧。"},{"pid":"31cbacdf19b8a8328047d5609998f2dbf3530644","tid":1402711,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e428d303a515d3e278d0eebd9c9271e000b3b38e","tid":1402711,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山已點起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7922c0aeaedfca332a8382b59ba3261546c70421","tid":1402711,"uid":235139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:57:53.000Z","msg":"支持，十八區的話我日日同你發一次夢都仲得。"},{"pid":"79a6280190017c82c481c353890bd4bd1cab7893","tid":1402711,"uid":189671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"唔一定一嚟十八區，可以試下幾區先，冇記錯沙田，天水圍，黃大仙，葵涌班街坊幾正氣下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fb763897b1f0209372ca4bf945effa8afac852","tid":1402711,"uid":189671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f